<link href="~/css/site - Copy.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<form method="post">
    <h1 class="display-1 mb-4 text-center">Severity Scores</h1>
    <p>Learn the factors that contribute to crash severity scores. Watch the video to learn more about the consequences of severe car crashes.</p>

    <div class="card-deck">

        <div class="card text-black bg-light">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="card-title">1 - No Injury</h4>
                @*<p class="card-text">This card has supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content.</p>*@

            </div>
            <button name="severity" value="1" type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-primary medbtncole">Results</button>

        </div>

        <div class="card text-black bg-light">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="card-title">2 - Possible Injury</h4>
                @*<p class="card-text">This card has supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content.</p>*@
            </div>
            <button name="severity" value="2" type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-primary medbtncole">Results</button>
        </div>

        <div class="card text-black bg-light">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="card-title">3 - Suspected Minor Injury</h4>
                @*<p class="card-text">This is a wider card with supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content. This card has even longer content than the first to show that equal height action.</p>*@
            </div>
            <button name="severity" value="3" type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-primary medbtncole ">Results</button>
        </div>

        <div class="card text-black bg-light">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="card-title">4 - Suspected Serious Injury</h4>
                @*<p class="card-text">This card has supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content.</p>*@
            </div>
            <button name="severity" value="4" type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-primary medbtncole ">Results</button>
        </div>

        <div class="card text-black bg-light">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="card-title">5 - Fatal</h4>
                @*<p class="card-text">This card has supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content.</p>*@
            </div>
            <button name="severity" value="5" type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-primary medbtncole ">Results</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <br />
    <br />
    <br />

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-3"></div>
        <div class="col-3">
            <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bTb0hCt9FEI" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-5"></div>

</form>
